    "body": "From what I can tell this is a `yulInterpreter` bug.\r\n\r\nThe problem is that we pass the [scope of the caller to the called function](https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/blob/develop/test/tools/yulInterpreter/Interpreter.cpp#L251) which is wrong. We need to give it the scope of the called function.. not sure yet where to get that from. Looking into that now.",
